This paper focuses on multimodal language understanding for domestic service robots, which involves natural language processing (NLP), computer vision (CV), and robotics (RO). Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), followed by cs.RO (Robotics), cs.CV (Computer Vision), cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), and cs.LG (Machine Learning).
